Okay.

53:42.000 --> 53:43.375
No, no, no.

55:11.916 --> 55:13.374
BRUNO SULAK DRAPED IN JEWELS

55:13.375 --> 55:15.625
POLICE ON SULAK'S HEELS

56:22.416 --> 56:24.665
SULAK, THE STAR

