01:13:28.208 --> 01:13:31.666
<i>A commando group made up
of several armed individuals</i>

01:13:31.791 --> 01:13:35.874
<i>managed to free the now
infamous Bruno Sulak,</i>

01:13:35.875 --> 01:13:38.082
<i>as well as one of his accomplices,</i>

01:13:38.083 --> 01:13:41.790
<i>while they were being transferred
to the Lyon penitentiary.</i>

01:13:41.791 --> 01:13:43.665
<i>The fugitives are still at large,</i>

01:13:43.666 --> 01:13:47.333
<i>despite the large contingent
of police officers on their trail.</i>

01:13:48.958 --> 01:13:50.499
Thank you for today.

01:13:50.500 --> 01:13:52.749
<i>Moving on, the economy.</i>

01:13:52.750 --> 01:13:56.915
<i>EEC finance ministers are meeting
in Brussels</i>

01:13:56.916 --> 01:13:58.457
<i>to raise by one point</i>

01:13:58.458 --> 01:14:01.499
<i>the interest rate of central banks,</i>

01:14:01.500 --> 01:14:05.332
<i>which means that it will be
more difficult for households</i>

01:14:05.333 --> 01:14:07.833
<i>to get loans.</i>

01:14:09.500 --> 01:14:11.208
And they call us thieves.

01:14:22.083 --> 01:14:25.500
We need to go. Far away.

01:14:26.875 --> 01:14:29.458
Let's go someplace warm, please.

01:14:32.250 --> 01:14:33.750
In the sun.

01:14:34.333 --> 01:14:35.791
To Los Angeles!

01:14:38.000 --> 01:14:39.583
Chaplin's country.

01:14:40.208 --> 01:14:43.207
- Jim Morrison's country.
- Los Angeles.

01:14:43.208 --> 01:14:44.625
Land of jewels.

01:14:52.875 --> 01:14:54.541
Novica Zivkovic.

01:14:58.041 --> 01:14:59.791
That's my real name.

01:15:24.708 --> 01:15:28.458
- Hello?
<i>- Yes, pal. It's me, it's Bruno.</i>

01:15:29.916 --> 01:15:32.915
- Yes?
<i>- I'm sorry about the other day,</i>

01:15:32.916 --> 01:15:35.250
<i>we didn't have time for the rematch.</i>

01:15:36.125 --> 01:15:38.915
But we'll meet again very soon.

01:15:38.916 --> 01:15:41.040
Sooner than you think.

01:15:41.041 --> 01:15:42.415
I'm not so sure.

01:15:42.416 --> 01:15:44.541
Where are you? Are you in Paris?

01:15:45.500 --> 01:15:47.833
We could have a drink one of these days.

01:15:50.166 --> 01:15:52.040
Of course, you'll come alone.

01:15:52.041 --> 01:15:54.749
- Of course.
<i>- Sure, why not? I'll think about it.</i>

01:15:54.750 --> 01:15:57.416
I have to go.
I can't say "See you soon," pal.

01:16:00.625 --> 01:16:04.291
He's here, he's in Paris,
you need to find him!

01:16:24.791 --> 01:16:26.165
- Hello.
- Hello.

01:16:26.166 --> 01:16:27.708
- I'm here to report.
- Sure.

01:16:37.208 --> 01:16:40.000
POLICE STATION

01:16:41.625 --> 01:16:43.374
- Hello.
- Hello.

01:16:43.375 --> 01:16:45.625
- I'm here to report.
- Thank you.

01:17:01.625 --> 01:17:02.958
Annie Bragnier.

01:17:11.916 --> 01:17:15.082
- It's been two days. Move!
- Leave me alone.

01:17:15.083 --> 01:17:17.000
- No.
- Come on.

01:17:17.666 --> 01:17:20.040
<i>It'll put a smile on your face</i>

01:17:20.041 --> 01:17:22.291
<i>Come on, Annie</i>

01:17:22.416 --> 01:17:24.708
I'll make you a wonderful meal.

01:17:24.833 --> 01:17:27.750
<i>Oh, yes, my little Annie</i>

01:17:37.791 --> 01:17:40.875
- Hello.
- Annie Bragnier, reporting.

01:18:04.708 --> 01:18:07.582
- What's up?
- It's been so long!

01:18:07.583 --> 01:18:08.957
Are you ready?

01:18:08.958 --> 01:18:12.500
- Ready? We're going on vacation.
- Really?

01:18:31.125 --> 01:18:32.916
My love, what are you drinking?

01:18:34.791 --> 01:18:37.415
- How about some ice cream?
- Sure.

01:18:37.416 --> 01:18:39.874
- Pistachio.
- Pistachio.

01:18:39.875 --> 01:18:41.624
I'll get you one.

01:18:41.625 --> 01:18:44.166
- Want some ice cream?
- No, I'm good.

01:19:13.500 --> 01:19:15.208
Steve?

01:19:16.750 --> 01:19:18.416
Are we on vacation?

01:19:39.291 --> 01:19:40.666
What are you doing?

01:19:40.791 --> 01:19:43.375
I'm leaving, I've had enough. Move.

01:19:45.125 --> 01:19:46.458
Why?

01:19:48.541 --> 01:19:49.791
Why?

01:19:51.541 --> 01:19:53.541
I thought we were on vacation.

01:19:55.291 --> 01:19:59.207
We can be on vacation and work.

01:19:59.208 --> 01:20:00.583
I don't think it's funny.

01:20:05.000 --> 01:20:07.125
It's gonna end badly, you know?

01:20:07.916 --> 01:20:09.415
What are you afraid of?

01:20:09.416 --> 01:20:12.124
Nothing. I just don't want it
to end badly.

01:20:12.125 --> 01:20:14.290
Actually, I am afraid for you and Steve.

01:20:14.291 --> 01:20:16.624
See, you're afraid.
Do you want me to quit?

01:20:16.625 --> 01:20:17.957
I never asked you to quit.

01:20:17.958 --> 01:20:19.875
But I'll never ask you to keep doing it.

01:20:21.333 --> 01:20:23.249
So what do you want, then?

01:20:23.250 --> 01:20:25.750
I just want a few days of peace with you.

01:20:26.125 --> 01:20:28.790
You were gone to America for months.

01:20:28.791 --> 01:20:31.874
Just the two of us, for two days,
just two minutes, okay?

01:20:31.875 --> 01:20:34.333
- Stop.
- When are you gonna stop?

01:20:36.625 --> 01:20:38.790
Don't you see? I won't be there.

01:20:38.791 --> 01:20:41.333
I won't be there when you get arrested.

01:20:43.458 --> 01:20:46.125
Honestly, the Cartier in Cannes,
you must both be insane.

01:20:46.250 --> 01:20:49.291
We won't get arrested. Annie, come on.

01:20:53.458 --> 01:20:55.083
Okay?

01:21:03.750 --> 01:21:05.541
We won't get arrested.

01:21:09.625 --> 01:21:10.708
Annie!

01:22:34.208 --> 01:22:36.124
<i>Forty million francs worth of jewels.</i>

01:22:36.125 --> 01:22:39.499
<i>That's the loot of the robbers
who attacked Cartier in Cannes yesterday.</i>

01:22:39.500 --> 01:22:41.749
<i>The two robbers were identified
by the police.</i>

01:22:41.750 --> 01:22:45.666
<i>The man is a Yugoslavian,
Bruno Sulak, "The Legionnaire",</i>

01:22:46.083 --> 01:22:47.457
<i>he already took part in</i>

01:22:47.458 --> 01:22:50.916
<i>- in most of the robberies.</i>
- Annie! Bruno is on TV!

01:22:55.916 --> 01:23:00.540
<i>Around 12.30 p.m.,
two people came in together.</i>

01:23:00.541 --> 01:23:02.624
<i>About one minute apart.</i>

01:23:02.625 --> 01:23:04.249
<i>And they asked to see some pieces.</i>

01:23:04.250 --> 01:23:06.707
<i>Thanks to one of the employees' testimony,</i>

01:23:06.708 --> 01:23:08.957
<i>the robbers were easily identified.</i>

01:23:08.958 --> 01:23:12.207
<i>They're two Yugoslavians,
Bruno Sulak and Radisa Jovanovic.</i>

01:23:12.208 --> 01:23:15.958
<i>Bruno Sulak, "The Legionnaire",
is well-known to the police.</i>

01:23:17.041 --> 01:23:18.582
<i>Bruno Sulak.</i>

01:23:18.583 --> 01:23:20.165
<i>Bruno Sulak, the offender...</i>

01:23:20.166 --> 01:23:21.832
<i>The uncatchable thief...</i>

01:23:21.833 --> 01:23:23.499
<i>The man who escaped twice...</i>

01:23:23.500 --> 01:23:26.790
<i>The modern-day Arsène Lupin...</i>

01:23:26.791 --> 01:23:29.166
<i>...28 years old, hates violence.</i>

01:23:29.666 --> 01:23:33.582
<i>The loot is said to be worth
dozens of billions...</i>

01:23:33.583 --> 01:23:38.124
<i>Sulak's heists have made him
the biggest public enemy number one.</i>

01:23:38.125 --> 01:23:40.249
<i>A very gentle man.</i>

01:23:40.250 --> 01:23:43.625
<i>He's never, ever fired a gun.</i>

01:23:43.875 --> 01:23:46.791
<i>That's a rule he always follows.</i>

01:23:49.166 --> 01:23:51.875
Yes? Boss! Sulak!

01:23:52.541 --> 01:23:55.415
<i>So, how about that drink?
Are you free today?</i>

01:23:55.416 --> 01:23:57.375
<i>Noon at your café?</i>

01:23:57.833 --> 01:23:59.999
<i>But you come alone, right?
You promised.</i>

01:24:00.000 --> 01:24:01.333
<i>Of course, I promise.</i>

01:24:01.458 --> 01:24:05.124
<i>If you ever find me in the street,
don't worry, I never carry a gun.</i>

01:24:05.125 --> 01:24:07.540
<i>- You won't shoot me?
- I never carry a gun.</i>

01:24:07.541 --> 01:24:09.874
<i>If we find you, you won't shoot at us?</i>

01:24:09.875 --> 01:24:11.291
<i>No.</i>

01:24:13.833 --> 01:24:17.291
Then let me tell you something,
if I can't find you, I'll quit.

01:24:18.083 --> 01:24:21.124
If you hear that I've quit,
it will be your fault.

01:24:21.125 --> 01:24:23.666
<i>- In the news?</i>
- Exactly.

01:24:24.750 --> 01:24:26.916
- Okay? See you soon.
<i>- See you soon, pal.</i>

01:25:13.916 --> 01:25:16.208
Police! Hands in the air! Don't move.

01:25:18.166 --> 01:25:19.833
Take off your helmet.

01:25:21.083 --> 01:25:23.374
- Who the hell are you?
- Nobody.

01:25:23.375 --> 01:25:25.999
I was asked to deliver this bag
to some guy outside the café.

01:25:26.000 --> 01:25:27.416
That's all. I'm a delivery guy.

01:25:29.583 --> 01:25:32.541
- Who asked you to deliver that?
- The baker.

01:25:34.875 --> 01:25:36.124
Book this little clown.

01:25:36.125 --> 01:25:38.041
- Come on.
- I didn't do anything.

01:25:39.416 --> 01:25:41.916
Call off the crew. Back to the station.

01:26:01.875 --> 01:26:03.457
Hands on the wheel.

01:26:03.458 --> 01:26:06.208
Don't do anything stupid,
drive around the square. Come on.

01:26:13.750 --> 01:26:15.166
How are you doing?

01:26:17.375 --> 01:26:19.708
I'm good. How are you?

01:26:21.666 --> 01:26:24.707
- Did you enjoy Cannes?
- Yes, it was ballsy.

01:26:24.708 --> 01:26:26.250
You're impressed, aren't you?

01:26:27.666 --> 01:26:30.999
You gave me your word,
but you were far from being alone.

01:26:31.000 --> 01:26:34.624
You know how the big bosses are.
I can't do what I want.

01:26:34.625 --> 01:26:36.583
I told you on the train,
you've got no power.

01:26:37.791 --> 01:26:39.208
Look in front of you.

01:26:42.833 --> 01:26:44.083
I won.

01:26:44.541 --> 01:26:46.957
You lost. I'm out of here.

01:26:46.958 --> 01:26:48.500
I quit.

01:26:50.000 --> 01:26:51.583
Look, I have more money than Borg.

01:26:53.333 --> 01:26:55.416
And I never played tennis.

01:26:58.291 --> 01:27:02.666
You'll get bored on vacation.
I'll see you again.

01:27:13.708 --> 01:27:15.916
Okay, stop the car, I'm feeling nauseous.

01:27:23.416 --> 01:27:24.375
Here.

01:27:24.833 --> 01:27:26.290
Give this to Annie

01:27:26.291 --> 01:27:29.040
and tell her to call this number
from a payphone.

01:27:29.041 --> 01:27:30.750
Everything's inside. Tickets, cash.

01:27:32.583 --> 01:27:33.708
No problem.

01:27:34.458 --> 01:27:36.916
- Do you have what I wanted?
- Yes.

01:27:40.125 --> 01:27:41.125
Here.

01:27:42.791 --> 01:27:44.083
Is it the Pole?

01:27:44.833 --> 01:27:47.124
He's in jail.
It's another guy, from Marseille.

01:27:47.125 --> 01:27:48.208
DRIVING LICENSE

01:27:50.458 --> 01:27:51.999
It's terrible work.

01:27:52.000 --> 01:27:53.624
And it's not cheap.

01:27:53.625 --> 01:27:55.082
But you're famous.

01:27:55.083 --> 01:27:57.499
People are scared.
They're asking for a lot of money.

01:27:57.500 --> 01:27:59.333
Yes, I know.

01:28:04.250 --> 01:28:07.458
I'll call you when I'm in Rio.
Will you join us there?

01:28:09.833 --> 01:28:12.500
In Rio? I would absolutely love it.

01:28:16.833 --> 01:28:19.625
- Cheers, my friend.
- Cheers.

01:28:27.166 --> 01:28:29.332
<i>- Hello?
- My love.</i>

01:28:29.333 --> 01:28:32.040
<i>My love, how are you? Where are you?</i>

01:28:32.041 --> 01:28:34.083
<i>Too far, I'm too far away from you.</i>

01:28:35.500 --> 01:28:37.707
<i>I'm about to cross the Italian border.</i>

01:28:37.708 --> 01:28:39.874
<i>We're going somewhere warm, to Brazil.</i>

01:28:39.875 --> 01:28:41.082
<i>Brazil?</i>

01:28:41.083 --> 01:28:44.624
<i>Yes, you and me.
We're going to spend all this money.</i>

01:28:44.625 --> 01:28:47.624
<i>We're gonna go to the beach,
we'll make love, and laugh.</i>

01:28:47.625 --> 01:28:50.874
<i>We'll eat good food, bask in the sun,
have a lot of babies.</i>

01:28:50.875 --> 01:28:52.957
<i>We need to stop hiding.</i>

01:28:52.958 --> 01:28:54.707
<i>We'll stay stuck together forever.</i>

01:28:54.708 --> 01:28:56.082
ID check.

01:28:56.083 --> 01:28:57.915
<i>- I like that idea.
- Really?</i>

01:28:57.916 --> 01:28:59.332
<i>Yes.</i>

01:28:59.333 --> 01:29:00.790
<i>- Will you join me?
- Yes.</i>

01:29:00.791 --> 01:29:02.250
<i>- Are we leaving?
- Yes.</i>

01:29:02.833 --> 01:29:05.083
<i>- See you tomorrow, my love.
- See you tomorrow.</i>

01:29:07.083 --> 01:29:08.624
- Hello.
<i>- Buongiorno.</i>

01:29:08.625 --> 01:29:11.791
Customs check.
Turn off the engine, please.

01:29:13.166 --> 01:29:14.875
Do you have your ID?

01:29:22.833 --> 01:29:24.125
Thank you.

01:29:33.083 --> 01:29:36.000
Please step out of the vehicle
and follow me.

01:29:43.500 --> 01:29:46.458
FRENCH CUSTOMS

01:29:48.250 --> 01:29:51.458
I don't understand,
why a Belgian passport?

01:29:51.791 --> 01:29:54.749
Why? The passport is Belgian
because my father is Belgian

01:29:54.750 --> 01:29:56.624
and my mother is Italian.
It's simple.

01:29:56.625 --> 01:30:00.041
- The dad's Belgian, the mom's...
- I get that.

01:30:00.541 --> 01:30:02.916
But I don't like your passport.

01:30:03.041 --> 01:30:05.249
So I'm waiting to hear back
from the embassy.

01:30:05.250 --> 01:30:07.374
They will tell you the same thing,
Are you drunk?

01:30:07.375 --> 01:30:08.582
I've wasted too much time.

01:30:08.583 --> 01:30:11.082
I have to go to Italy,
I'm expected in Sicily.

01:30:11.083 --> 01:30:13.332
I don't understand anything!

01:30:13.333 --> 01:30:15.540
Please lower your voice.

01:30:15.541 --> 01:30:17.208
Okay?

01:30:19.708 --> 01:30:22.207
There's a woman somewhere else
waiting for me.

01:30:22.208 --> 01:30:25.124
- What is he saying?
- It's about a woman.

01:30:25.125 --> 01:30:27.708
And I didn't tell my wife.

01:30:27.875 --> 01:30:29.249
Love.

01:30:29.250 --> 01:30:32.874
Yes, it's adultery.
He's going to see a woman in Italy.

01:30:32.875 --> 01:30:34.665
This gentleman is married, is that it?

01:30:34.666 --> 01:30:37.790
But that doesn't explain the passport.

01:30:37.791 --> 01:30:38.916
I don't like it.

01:30:39.041 --> 01:30:41.582
But there's nothing to understand.
I've wasted too much time.

01:30:41.583 --> 01:30:42.875
chatting here in this room.

01:30:43.041 --> 01:30:46.832
Please. I can't wait any longer,
I have to go to Italy.

01:30:46.833 --> 01:30:49.375
This woman is waiting for me. I can't...

01:30:52.416 --> 01:30:53.583
Oh, Bruno.

01:30:54.958 --> 01:30:57.374
Looking good.
Being blond suits you.

01:30:57.375 --> 01:30:58.750
Thank you, gentlemen.

01:30:59.166 --> 01:31:01.583
Let's go.
It's over, let's go back to Paris.

01:31:03.125 --> 01:31:04.166
By train?

01:31:28.000 --> 01:31:29.333
Can I open the window?

01:31:29.916 --> 01:31:31.125
Sure.

01:32:00.250 --> 01:32:04.000
<i>Therefore, in the name
of the French people,</i>

01:32:04.916 --> 01:32:07.750
<i>the court sentences you
to nine years in prison.</i>

01:32:08.875 --> 01:32:11.833
Which you will serve
in the Fleury-Mérogis Penitentiary.

01:32:12.541 --> 01:32:14.250
The session is adjourned.

01:32:42.041 --> 01:32:43.541
<i>Let's go get Bruno.</i>

01:32:45.833 --> 01:32:48.625
<i>I'll wait for him at 6:00 a.m.
at the heliport.</i>

01:32:49.291 --> 01:32:51.250
<i>Yes, it's my only chance!</i>

01:32:51.958 --> 01:32:54.208
Come on, don't wait.

01:33:04.125 --> 01:33:06.707
<i>You have to be drunk always.</i>

01:33:06.708 --> 01:33:10.333
<i>That's everything.
That's the only question.</i>

01:33:11.833 --> 01:33:15.082
<i>For you not to feel the horrible
burden of time, breaking your shoulders,</i>

01:33:15.083 --> 01:33:19.124
<i>and bending you down to earth,
you must be drunk without respite.</i>

01:33:19.125 --> 01:33:20.624
<i>But drunk on what?</i>

01:33:20.625 --> 01:33:23.916
<i>Wine, poetry,</i>

01:33:24.750 --> 01:33:27.791
<i>Or virtue. At your leisure.</i>

01:33:28.333 --> 01:33:32.082
<i>And if, sometimes, on the steps of a
palace, on the green grass of a ditch,</i>

01:33:32.083 --> 01:33:35.416
<i>in the dreary solitude of your room,
you wake up,</i>

01:33:36.041 --> 01:33:38.875
<i>with your drunkenness
diminished, disappeared,</i>

01:33:39.875 --> 01:33:43.207
<i>ask the wind, the wave,
the star, the bird, the clock,</i>

01:33:43.208 --> 01:33:47.165
<i>all that laughs, all that moans and all
that flees, all that sings, speaks,</i>

01:33:47.166 --> 01:33:50.915
<i>ask what time it is, and the wind,
the wave, the bird, the clock</i>

01:33:50.916 --> 01:33:53.375
<i>will answer you:
"'It's time to get drunk.'</i>

01:33:54.291 --> 01:33:56.665
<i>So as not to be time's martyred slaves,</i>

01:33:56.666 --> 01:33:59.125
<i>get drunk, get drunk without respite".</i>
- My love.

01:34:01.208 --> 01:34:04.833
<i>"On wine, poetry, love,</i>

01:34:05.375 --> 01:34:08.250
<i>"or virtue, at your leisure."</i>

01:34:10.375 --> 01:34:12.875
I'm not even there to hold you in my arms.

01:34:46.041 --> 01:34:47.458
Here.

01:35:03.833 --> 01:35:06.458
- You're hungry.
- Jail food...

01:35:07.583 --> 01:35:09.250
I can't even go to the cafeteria.

01:35:09.708 --> 01:35:12.291
- Why?
- Beats me.

01:35:12.791 --> 01:35:16.166
They must be scared
I'd hide a saw in coffee grounds.

01:35:19.500 --> 01:35:20.958
I heard about Steve.

01:35:27.875 --> 01:35:31.833
He was executed.
They didn't give him a chance.

01:35:33.291 --> 01:35:36.416
Abolition of the death penalty my ass.

01:35:36.958 --> 01:35:39.416
Do you agree with that?
You and your little colleagues?

01:35:39.791 --> 01:35:41.375
It wasn't my team.

01:35:41.833 --> 01:35:43.291
I handed in my resignation.

01:35:50.875 --> 01:35:53.083
- You're not a cop anymore?
- No.

01:35:53.875 --> 01:35:57.250
- Because of that?
- Amongst other things.

01:36:00.000 --> 01:36:02.874
Since you're in jail,
I don't feel like chasing anyone else.

01:36:02.875 --> 01:36:05.375
If you think that I'll stay locked up...

01:36:10.416 --> 01:36:12.375
Admit it, you'll miss me.

01:36:18.500 --> 01:36:19.791
What are you gonna do now?

01:36:23.041 --> 01:36:27.708
I'm taking some time
to travel, read, write.

01:36:28.375 --> 01:36:32.915
To write detective novels,
that's a retired cop thing.

01:36:32.916 --> 01:36:34.500
Sure, why not?

01:36:39.291 --> 01:36:41.041
Keep your head down.

01:36:43.916 --> 01:36:45.166
Do your time.

01:36:45.916 --> 01:36:48.250
You're still young,
you still have a lot to experience.

01:36:50.250 --> 01:36:51.666
Why are you telling me this?

01:36:53.291 --> 01:36:55.583
They won't go easy on you
if you go too far.

01:37:01.416 --> 01:37:04.583
You've given me an idea.
Maybe I'll write a book too.

01:37:05.708 --> 01:37:08.083
- About what?
- Freedom.

01:37:08.458 --> 01:37:12.416
Love, the Mediterranean, life.
That's all I'll say or you'll steal it.

01:37:13.000 --> 01:37:15.291
Visit's over. Let's go, Sulak.

01:37:23.083 --> 01:37:26.041
I don't even know your first name.

01:37:29.833 --> 01:37:31.083
Georges.

01:37:32.333 --> 01:37:33.958
It's Georges.

01:37:35.750 --> 01:37:38.416
- Bye, Georges.
- Bye, Bruno.

01:37:40.875 --> 01:37:42.416
Take care of yourself.

01:37:42.958 --> 01:37:44.499
Oh, you know me.

01:37:44.500 --> 01:37:46.707
Okay, let's go.

01:37:46.708 --> 01:37:50.250
- Sorry, it's not easy here.
- Get up.

01:37:50.791 --> 01:37:52.250
Come on.

01:37:55.250 --> 01:37:56.833
Will you come back?

01:37:59.333 --> 01:38:01.374
- Yes.
- Let's go.

01:38:01.375 --> 01:38:02.708
Ciao.

01:38:38.583 --> 01:38:40.625
We'll follow the plan.
I trust you.

01:38:41.166 --> 01:38:43.166
<i>The walkie-talkie and the open door.</i>

01:38:48.000 --> 01:38:50.291
<i>I'm taking a lot of risks for Sulak.</i>

01:38:52.250 --> 01:38:56.458
Wait for my last call
and my final instructions. Later.

01:39:07.458 --> 01:39:10.832
Everything's ready, Bruno.
Follow the plan to the letter.

01:39:10.833 --> 01:39:13.875
If there's a problem, get back
to your cell. Good luck.

01:39:38.666 --> 01:39:40.499
I'm in the main corridor.

01:39:40.500 --> 01:39:41.750
<i>Okay, Bruno.</i>

01:40:01.500 --> 01:40:04.415
- It's locked.
<i>- It should be open.</i>

01:40:04.416 --> 01:40:05.665
It's closed, what do I do?

01:40:05.666 --> 01:40:09.458
<i>I don't understand. I left instructions.
I arranged it all.</i>

01:40:11.458 --> 01:40:13.124
<i>Bruno? I can't hear you.</i>

01:40:13.125 --> 01:40:15.750
<i>If it's not going to plan,
go back to your cell.</i>

01:40:34.708 --> 01:40:37.625
- What do you want?
- Americano, two sugars.

01:40:41.666 --> 01:40:43.500
- Two sugars.
- Yes.

01:41:05.875 --> 01:41:07.416
<i>Bruno?</i>

01:41:16.000 --> 01:41:17.665
Get out.

01:41:17.666 --> 01:41:21.875
Get out of there.
What are you doing with this?

01:42:15.875 --> 01:42:17.291
<i>My love,</i>

01:42:18.041 --> 01:42:20.374
<i>once again, I escaped in my dream</i>

01:42:20.375 --> 01:42:22.666
<i>to fall asleep near your warm body.</i>

01:42:23.958 --> 01:42:25.625
<i>A peaceful feeling.</i>

01:42:26.583 --> 01:42:29.000
<i>Heavy body, light mind.</i>

01:42:29.166 --> 01:42:31.790
<i>I fly, I float.</i>

01:42:31.791 --> 01:42:35.250
<i>I can't feel gravity in the night
that surrounds me with your smell.</i>

01:42:35.833 --> 01:42:37.540
<i>I'm not there anymore.</i>

01:42:37.541 --> 01:42:40.000
<i>I'm disappearing and finally...</i>

01:42:40.541 --> 01:42:43.416
<i>Finally, I find you forever.</i>

01:42:43.625 --> 01:42:45.416
<i>Finally.</i>

01:43:01.458 --> 01:43:04.165
<i>It has to end one day.</i>

01:43:04.166 --> 01:43:07.541
<i>Anyway, I would not have made
a very honorable old man.</i>

01:43:09.041 --> 01:43:11.875
<i>But you know, it is my destiny.</i>

01:43:12.000 --> 01:43:13.541
<i>I know that.</i>

